category: Elements or accessories of a physical book
explanation: All tokens except 'E-reader' are either a physical component of a printed book or an accessory specifically used with a printed book. An E-reader is a digital device for reading.

All listed battles, except for the Battle of Midway, were predominantly land-based military engagements. The Battle of Midway was a decisive naval battle fought primarily by aircraft carriers in the Pacific Ocean.
All tokens except 'MIRROR' are palindromes, meaning they read the same forwards and backwards.
